      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776399446781,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Main game modules:\n\n`Environment.tsx`\nWorld meshes, pickups, hazards,\ndroids, enemy lasers, decoration\n\n`Projectiles.tsx`\nPlayer bullets and hit detection\n\n`FollowCamera.tsx`\nSmooth chase camera\n\n`HUD.tsx` + `MenuScreen.tsx`\nUI overlays\n\n`useKeyboard.ts`\nInput state ref\n\n`types.ts`\nGameData, entity types,\nELEVATION_LEVELS, initial state",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Main game modules:\n\n`Environment.tsx`\nWorld meshes, pickups, hazards,\ndroids, enemy lasers, decoration\n\n`Projectiles.tsx`\nPlayer bullets and hit detection\n\n`FollowCamera.tsx`\nSmooth chase camera\n\n`HUD.tsx` + `MenuScreen.tsx`\nUI overlays\n\n`useKeyboard.ts`\nInput state ref\n\n`types.ts`\nGameData, entity types,\nELEVATION_LEVELS, initial state",
      "autoResize": false,
