      "text": "Model normalization examples:\nEnemy UFOs scale against orb base size\nGalaxies scale using `galaxy.scale / galaxyBaseSizes[model]`\nUseful when GLBs were exported at different units",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
